## 9. Hardening Requirements

### 9.1 Embed Model Consistency

On every collection write, verify embed model matches collection sentinel. If mismatch detected, STOP and report. Never write mismatched vectors.

If embed model must be upgraded:
1. Create new collections with `_v2` suffix
2. Re-embed all points from old collection into new
3. Verify point counts match
4. Rename (or update config to point to new collections)
5. Archive old collections, do not delete for 30 days

### 9.2 Schema Drift Monitoring

Weekly Celery task. Query Qdrant for relationship type values in memory collection payload. Compare against `FLAT_TAXONOMY`. Output to `./logs/schema_drift.log`:

